CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 25, 2008

[Cite as 0212512008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-721.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2006-1403. State ex rel. Ebersole v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 05AP-302, 2006-0hio-3441. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
